Subject: False positive
Description: We currently have a policy that checks for SSN - there are files on the remote network file share that are being flagged for violation - after close manual inspection we have determine that these files are false positive.  User even tried to authroize but was denied - please help us ensure that we have the ability to whitelist this or that the scanning is correctly setup.
Solution_Comment__c: Closing ticket as resolved after whitelisting the time machine locations that were causing too many scans and erroring out the time machine backup.
